---
---
<section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-image">
    <img src="/images/author.png" alt="Author in kitchen" />
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <span class="about-label">welcome!</span>
    <h2>Hey, I'm Sarah!</h2>
    <p>I believe healthy eating should be simple, delicious, and stress-free. Here you'll find wholesome recipes and easy meal plans to help you feel your best — without spending hours in the kitchen.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-btn">Read More →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    min-height: 500px;
    background: var(--color-subscribe-bg);
  }
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 50px;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .about-label {
    font-family: 'Dancing Script', 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-links);
  }
  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 420px;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 13px 26px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    width: fit-content;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary-text);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }
  .cta-btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .about-image img {
      max-height: 380px;
    }
    .about-text {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
